title: Vitali Belichenko
text:
Vitali Sergeyevich Belichenko (; born 25 August 1982) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He played 3 seasons in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20Chita">FC Chita</a> and <a href="FC%20Dynamo%20Barnaul">FC Dynamo Barnaul</a>.
